This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for face inpainting, which suggests that cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning algorithms (AI) and datasets related to multimedia (MM) and graphics (GR), which further supports these categories.
